## 🚀 Quick Start (5분)

### 빌드
```bash
cd stochastic-code-optimizer
mkdir -p build/bin

# 데모만 빌드
g++ -std=c++17 -O3 -o build/bin/demo src/main_demo.cpp

# 테스트만 빌드
g++ -std=c++17 -O3 -o build/bin/tests tests/unit_tests.cpp

# 모두 빌드
make build/bin/stochastic_optimizer_demo build/bin/unit_tests
```

### 실행
```bash
# 데모 실행
./build/bin/stochastic_optimizer_demo

# 테스트 실행
./build/bin/unit_tests
```

